snippet.title: Ship Graveyard Simulator 2  -  Xbox/PlayStation Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Ship Graveyard Simulator 2 launches on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S on  September 6th. In this game, players dismantle shipwrecks, with new features like dismantling large ship components. The console versions include the Warships DLC. Previously released on PC, the game is also coming to Nintendo Switch.

PlayStation 5: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10010588
Xbox Series X/S: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/ship-graveyard-simulator-2/9p5v8nv8mpl8
